Overview
"My Shopping List" is a web application designed to help users manage their shopping tasks and expenses. 

Features
Task Management: Add, and mark tasks.
Expense Tracking: Keep track of the cost associated with each task.
Real-time Balance: See your remaining budget as you add or complete tasks.
Visual Indicators: Completed tasks are visually distinguished for easy identification.
Responsive Design: The app is designed to work seamlessly on various screen sizes.
Installation
Clone the repository:
bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/deroldanop/DOMSBA-316
Open the project folder:
bash
Copy code
cd shopping-list-app
Open the index.html file in your web browser.
Usage
Enter the amount of money you have to spend.
Add tasks to your shopping list with associated costs.
Check off completed tasks to update your remaining budget.
Receive visual feedback on your spending status.
